  "detailed_description": "Fight to survive in extraterrestrial environments while scavenging weapons and ammo.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Horde Mode</h2>Defeat waves of enemies to earn money in order to upgrade your weapons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade/Salvage weapons<br></li><li>Experience being other planets/moons including Low Gravity<br></li><li>Realistic weapon interaction<br></li><li>Scavenge weapons/ammo with procedural spawning<br></li><li>Ammo belt for storing ammo and grabbing magazines<br></li><li>Weapon holsters for storing weapons<br></li><li>Touch pad locomotion<br></li><li>Haptic feedback when touching interactable objects<br></li><li>High definition textures and graphics with the power of Unity 5</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "Fight to survive in extraterrestrial environments while scavenging weapons and ammo.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Horde Mode</h2>Defeat waves of enemies to earn money in order to upgrade your weapons.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Upgrade/Salvage weapons<br></li><li>Experience being other planets/moons including Low Gravity<br></li><li>Realistic weapon interaction<br></li><li>Scavenge weapons/ammo with procedural spawning<br></li><li>Ammo belt for storing ammo and grabbing magazines<br></li><li>Weapon holsters for storing weapons<br></li><li>Touch pad locomotion<br></li><li>Haptic feedback when touching interactable objects<br></li><li>High definition textures and graphics with the power of Unity 5</li></ul>",
